ironmental planning agent\n*   Parks budget and operations agent\n*   Chat output from civic agents\n*   Parks department employee\n*   Accumulating conversation\n*   Instructions based on accumulated context and fresh insight\n\nThere are **8** entities that have more than one relation.", "answer": [5], "metadata": {"type": "fill_in_the_blank", "sub_type": "entities_have_more_than_one_relations", "difficulty": "basic"}, "setting": {"model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite-preview", "temperature": 0, "flag_async": true, "max_completion_tokens": 512, "prompt_type": "only_question"}, "token_usage": {"prompt_tokens": 1099, "thoughts_token": null, "completion_tokens": 480, "cached_content_tokens": null, "total_tokens": 1579}}
